{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I'm going to talk"},{"time":2000,"text":"about some of my discoveries"},{"time":4000,"text":"around the world through my work."},{"time":6000,"text":"These are not discoveries of planets"},{"time":8000,"text":"or new technologies"},{"time":10000,"text":"or science."},{"time":12000,"text":"They're discoveries of people"},{"time":14000,"text":"and the way people are, and new leadership."}]},{"cues":[{"time":19000,"text":"This is Benki."},{"time":21000,"text":"Benki is a leader of the Ashaninka Nation."},{"time":23000,"text":"His people live in Brazil"},{"time":25000,"text":"and in Peru."},{"time":27000,"text":"Benki comes from a village"},{"time":29000,"text":"so remote up in the Amazon"},{"time":31000,"text":"that to get there, either you have to fly"},{"time":34000,"text":"and land on water,"},{"time":36000,"text":"or go by canoe for several days."},{"time":39000,"text":"I met Benki three years ago in Sao Paulo"},{"time":42000,"text":"when I'd brought him and other leaders"},{"time":44000,"text":"from indigenous peoples"},{"time":46000,"text":"to meet with me and leaders from around the world,"},{"time":48000,"text":"because we wanted to learn from each other."},{"time":50000,"text":"We wanted to share our stories with each other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":54000,"text":"The Ashaninka people"},{"time":56000,"text":"are known throughout South America"},{"time":58000,"text":"for their dignity, their spirit"},{"time":61000,"text":"and their resistance,"},{"time":63000,"text":"starting with the Incas"},{"time":65000,"text":"and continuing through the 19th century"},{"time":67000,"text":"with the rubber tappers."},{"time":71000,"text":"Today's biggest threat to the Ashaninka people"},{"time":73000,"text":"and to Benki"},{"time":75000,"text":"comes from illegal logging --"},{"time":77000,"text":"the people who come into the beautiful forest"},{"time":79000,"text":"and cut down ancient mahogany trees,"},{"time":82000,"text":"float them down the river to world markets."},{"time":85000,"text":"Benki knew this."},{"time":87000,"text":"He could see what was happening to his forest, to his environment,"},{"time":90000,"text":"because he was taken under his grandfather's wing"},{"time":93000,"text":"when he was only two years old"},{"time":95000,"text":"to begin to learn about the forest"},{"time":98000,"text":"and the way of life of his people."},{"time":101000,"text":"His grandfather died when he was only 10."},{"time":104000,"text":"And at that young age, 10 years old,"},{"time":107000,"text":"Benki became the paje of his community."},{"time":110000,"text":"Now, in the Ashaninka tradition and culture,"},{"time":113000,"text":"the paje is the most important"},{"time":115000,"text":"person in the community."},{"time":117000,"text":"This is the person who contains within him"},{"time":120000,"text":"all the knowledge, all the wisdom"},{"time":123000,"text":"of centuries and centuries of life,"},{"time":126000,"text":"and not just about his people,"},{"time":129000,"text":"but about everything that his people's survival depended on:"},{"time":132000,"text":"the trees, the birds,"},{"time":134000,"text":"the water, the soil, the forest."},{"time":137000,"text":"So when he was only 10 and he became the paje,"},{"time":140000,"text":"he began to lead his people."},{"time":143000,"text":"He began to talk to them"},{"time":145000,"text":"about the forest that they needed to protect,"},{"time":147000,"text":"the way of life they needed to nurture."},{"time":150000,"text":"He explained to them"},{"time":152000,"text":"that it was not a question of survival of the fittest;"},{"time":155000,"text":"it was a question of understanding"},{"time":157000,"text":"what they needed to survive"},{"time":159000,"text":"and to protect that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":162000,"text":"Eight years later,"},{"time":164000,"text":"when he was a young man of 18,"},{"time":166000,"text":"Benki left the forest for the first time."},{"time":169000,"text":"He went 3,000 miles on an odyssey to Rio"},{"time":172000,"text":"to the Earth Summit"},{"time":174000,"text":"to tell the world what was happening"},{"time":176000,"text":"in his tiny, little corner."},{"time":178000,"text":"And he went because he hoped the world would listen."},{"time":181000,"text":"Some did, not everybody."},{"time":184000,"text":"But if you can imagine this young man"},{"time":186000,"text":"with his headdress and his flowing robe,"},{"time":188000,"text":"learning a new language, Portuguese,"},{"time":191000,"text":"not to mention English,"},{"time":193000,"text":"going to Rio,"},{"time":195000,"text":"building a bridge"},{"time":197000,"text":"to reach out to people he'd never met before --"},{"time":199000,"text":"a pretty hostile world."},{"time":201000,"text":"But he wasn't dismayed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":203000,"text":"Benki came back to his village full of ideas --"},{"time":206000,"text":"new technologies, new research,"},{"time":209000,"text":"new ways of understanding what was going on."},{"time":212000,"text":"Since that time,"},{"time":214000,"text":"he's continued to work with his people,"},{"time":216000,"text":"and not only the Ashaninka Nation,"},{"time":218000,"text":"but all the peoples of the Amazon and beyond."},{"time":221000,"text":"He's built schools"},{"time":223000,"text":"to teach children to care for the forest."},{"time":225000,"text":"Together, he's led the reforestation"},{"time":227000,"text":"of over 25 percent of the land"},{"time":229000,"text":"that had been destroyed by the loggers."},{"time":232000,"text":"He's created a cooperative"},{"time":234000,"text":"to help people diversify their livelihoods."},{"time":237000,"text":"And he's brought the internet and satellite technology"},{"time":239000,"text":"to the forest --"},{"time":241000,"text":"both so that people themselves"},{"time":243000,"text":"could monitor the deforestation,"},{"time":245000,"text":"but also that he could speak from the forest"},{"time":247000,"text":"to the rest of the world."},{"time":250000,"text":"If you were to meet Benki"},{"time":252000,"text":"and ask him, \"Why are you doing this?"},{"time":255000,"text":"Why are you putting yourself at risk?"},{"time":257000,"text":"Why are you making yourself vulnerable"},{"time":259000,"text":"to what is often a hostile world?\""},{"time":262000,"text":"he would tell you,"},{"time":264000,"text":"as he told me,"},{"time":266000,"text":"\"I asked myself,\" he said,"},{"time":269000,"text":"\"What did my grandparents and my great-grandparents do"},{"time":272000,"text":"to protect the forest for me?"},{"time":275000,"text":"And what am I doing?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":278000,"text":"So when I think of that,"},{"time":280000,"text":"I wonder what our grandchildren"},{"time":283000,"text":"and our great-grandchildren,"},{"time":285000,"text":"when they ask themselves that question,"},{"time":287000,"text":"I wonder how they will answer."},{"time":290000,"text":"For me, the world is veering"},{"time":292000,"text":"towards a future we don't much want"},{"time":295000,"text":"when we really think about it deep inside."},{"time":298000,"text":"It's a future we don't know the details of,"},{"time":301000,"text":"but it's a future that has signs,"},{"time":303000,"text":"just like Benki saw the signs around him."},{"time":307000,"text":"We know we are running out of what we need."},{"time":310000,"text":"We're running out of fresh water."},{"time":312000,"text":"We're running out of fossil fuels."},{"time":314000,"text":"We're running out of land."},{"time":316000,"text":"We know climate change is going to affect all of us."},{"time":319000,"text":"We don't know how, but we know it will."},{"time":322000,"text":"And we know that there will be more of us than ever before --"},{"time":325000,"text":"five times as many people in 40 years"},{"time":327000,"text":"than 60 years ago."},{"time":329000,"text":"We are running out of what we need."},{"time":332000,"text":"And we also know"},{"time":334000,"text":"that the world has changed in other ways,"},{"time":337000,"text":"that since 1960"},{"time":339000,"text":"there are one-third as many new countries"},{"time":342000,"text":"that exist as independent entities on the planet."},{"time":345000,"text":"Egos, systems of government --"},{"time":347000,"text":"figuring it out --"},{"time":349000,"text":"massive change."},{"time":351000,"text":"And in addition to that,"},{"time":353000,"text":"we know that five other really big countries"},{"time":355000,"text":"are going to have a say in the future,"},{"time":357000,"text":"a say we haven't even really started to hear yet --"},{"time":361000,"text":"China, India,"},{"time":363000,"text":"Russia, South Africa"},{"time":366000,"text":"and Benki's own Brazil,"},{"time":369000,"text":"where Benki got his civil rights"},{"time":371000,"text":"only in the 1988 constitution."}]},{"cues":[{"time":374000,"text":"But you know all that."},{"time":376000,"text":"You know more than Benki knew when he left his forest"},{"time":378000,"text":"and went 3,000 miles."},{"time":381000,"text":"You also know"},{"time":383000,"text":"that we can't just keep doing what we've always done,"},{"time":385000,"text":"because we'll get the results"},{"time":387000,"text":"we've always gotten."},{"time":389000,"text":"And this reminds me of something I understand"},{"time":391000,"text":"Lord Salisbury said to Queen Victoria over a hundred years ago,"},{"time":394000,"text":"when she was pressing him, \"Please change.\""},{"time":397000,"text":"He said, \"Change?"},{"time":399000,"text":"Why change?"},{"time":402000,"text":"Things are bad enough as they are.\""},{"time":407000,"text":"We have to change."},{"time":410000,"text":"It's imperative to me, when I look around the world,"},{"time":413000,"text":"that we need to change ourselves."},{"time":416000,"text":"We need new models of what it means to be a leader."},{"time":419000,"text":"We need new models"},{"time":421000,"text":"of being a leader and a human in the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":425000,"text":"I started life as a banker."},{"time":428000,"text":"Now I don't admit to that"},{"time":430000,"text":"to anybody but my very close friends."},{"time":433000,"text":"But for the past eight years,"},{"time":435000,"text":"I've done something completely different."},{"time":437000,"text":"My work has taken me around the world,"},{"time":439000,"text":"where I've had the real privilege"},{"time":441000,"text":"of meeting people like Benki"},{"time":444000,"text":"and many others who are making change happen"},{"time":446000,"text":"in their communities --"},{"time":448000,"text":"people who see the world differently,"},{"time":450000,"text":"who are asking different questions,"},{"time":452000,"text":"who have different answers,"},{"time":454000,"text":"who understand the filters that they wear"},{"time":457000,"text":"when they go out into the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":459000,"text":"This is Sanghamitra."},{"time":461000,"text":"Sanghamitra comes from Bangalore."},{"time":463000,"text":"I met Sanghamitra eight years ago"},{"time":466000,"text":"when I was in Bangalore"},{"time":468000,"text":"organizing a workshop with leaders of different NGO's"},{"time":471000,"text":"working in some of the hardest aspects of society."},{"time":475000,"text":"Sanghamitra didn't start life"},{"time":477000,"text":"as a leader of an NGO,"},{"time":479000,"text":"she started her career as university professor,"},{"time":482000,"text":"teaching English literature."},{"time":484000,"text":"But she realized that she was much too detached from the world doing that."},{"time":487000,"text":"She loved it, but she was too detached."},{"time":490000,"text":"And so in 1993,"},{"time":492000,"text":"a long time ago,"},{"time":494000,"text":"she decided to start a new organization"},{"time":497000,"text":"called Samraksha"},{"time":499000,"text":"focused on one of the hardest areas,"},{"time":501000,"text":"one of the hardest issues in India --"},{"time":503000,"text":"anywhere in the world at the time --"},{"time":505000,"text":"HIV/AIDS."},{"time":507000,"text":"Since that time, Samraksha has grown"},{"time":509000,"text":"from strength to strength"},{"time":511000,"text":"and is now one of the leading health NGO's in India."},{"time":514000,"text":"But if you just think about the state of the world"},{"time":517000,"text":"and knowledge of HIV/AIDS"},{"time":519000,"text":"in 1993 --"},{"time":521000,"text":"in India at that time it was skyrocketing"},{"time":523000,"text":"and nobody understood why,"},{"time":525000,"text":"and everyone was actually very, very afraid."},{"time":528000,"text":"Today there are still three million"},{"time":530000,"text":"HIV-positive people in India."},{"time":533000,"text":"That's the second largest population in the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":537000,"text":"When I asked Sanghamitra,"},{"time":539000,"text":"\"How did you get from English literature"},{"time":541000,"text":"to HIV/AIDS?\""},{"time":543000,"text":"not an obvious path,"},{"time":545000,"text":"she said to me,"},{"time":547000,"text":"\"It's all connected."},{"time":550000,"text":"Literature makes one sensitive,"},{"time":552000,"text":"sensitive to people,"},{"time":554000,"text":"to their dreams and to their ideas.\""},{"time":556000,"text":"Since that time, under her leadership,"},{"time":558000,"text":"Samraksha has been a pioneer"},{"time":560000,"text":"in all fields related"},{"time":562000,"text":"to HIV/AIDS."},{"time":564000,"text":"They have respite homes, the first,"},{"time":566000,"text":"the first care centers,"},{"time":568000,"text":"the first counseling services --"},{"time":570000,"text":"and not just in urban, 7-million-population Bangalore,"},{"time":573000,"text":"but in the hardest to reach villages"},{"time":575000,"text":"in the state of Karnataka."},{"time":577000,"text":"Even that wasn't enough."},{"time":579000,"text":"She wanted to change policy at the government level."},{"time":582000,"text":"10 of their programs that she pioneered"},{"time":584000,"text":"are now government policy and funded by the government."},{"time":588000,"text":"They take care of 20,000-odd people today"},{"time":591000,"text":"in over 1,000 villages around Karnataka."}]},{"cues":[{"time":594000,"text":"She works with people like Murali Krishna."},{"time":597000,"text":"Murali Krishna comes from one of those villages."},{"time":600000,"text":"He lost his wife to AIDS a couple of years ago,"},{"time":603000,"text":"and he's HIV-positive."},{"time":605000,"text":"But he saw the work, the care,"},{"time":607000,"text":"the compassion"},{"time":609000,"text":"that Sanghamitra and her team brought to the village,"},{"time":612000,"text":"and he wanted to be part of it."},{"time":614000,"text":"He's a Leaders' Quest fellow, and that helps him with his work."},{"time":617000,"text":"They've pioneered a different approach to villages."},{"time":619000,"text":"Instead of handing out information in pamphlets,"},{"time":621000,"text":"as is so often the case,"},{"time":623000,"text":"they bring theater troupes,"},{"time":625000,"text":"songs, music, dance."},{"time":628000,"text":"And they sit around,"},{"time":630000,"text":"and they talk about dreams."}]},{"cues":[{"time":632000,"text":"Sanghamitra told me just last week --"},{"time":634000,"text":"she had just come back from two weeks in the villages,"},{"time":637000,"text":"and she had a real breakthrough."},{"time":639000,"text":"They were sitting in a circle, talking about the dreams for the village."},{"time":642000,"text":"And the young women in the village"},{"time":645000,"text":"spoke up and said, \"We've changed our dream."},{"time":648000,"text":"Our dream"},{"time":650000,"text":"is for our partners, our husbands,"},{"time":652000,"text":"not to be given to us because of a horoscope,"},{"time":655000,"text":"but to be given to us"},{"time":657000,"text":"because they've been tested for HIV.\""},{"time":660000,"text":"If you are lucky enough to meet Sanghamitra"},{"time":663000,"text":"and ask her why and how,"},{"time":666000,"text":"how have you achieved so much?"},{"time":670000,"text":"She would look at you"},{"time":672000,"text":"and very quietly, very softly say,"},{"time":675000,"text":"\"It just happened."},{"time":678000,"text":"It's the spirit inside.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":682000,"text":"This is Dr. Fan Jianchuan."},{"time":685000,"text":"Jianchuan comes from Sichuan Province"},{"time":687000,"text":"in southwest China."},{"time":689000,"text":"He was born in 1957,"},{"time":691000,"text":"and you can imagine what his childhood"},{"time":693000,"text":"looked like and felt like,"},{"time":695000,"text":"and what his life has been like"},{"time":697000,"text":"over the last 50 tumultuous years."},{"time":700000,"text":"He's been a soldier, a teacher,"},{"time":702000,"text":"a politician, a vice-mayor"},{"time":704000,"text":"and a business man."},{"time":706000,"text":"But if you sat down and asked him, \"Who are you really,"},{"time":709000,"text":"and what do you do?\""},{"time":711000,"text":"He would tell you, \"I'm a collector,"},{"time":714000,"text":"and I curate a museum.\""},{"time":716000,"text":"I was lucky; I had heard about him for years,"},{"time":718000,"text":"and I finally met him earlier this year"},{"time":720000,"text":"at his museum in Chengdu."}]},{"cues":[{"time":723000,"text":"He's been a collector all of his life,"},{"time":726000,"text":"starting when he was four or five in the early 1960's."},{"time":729000,"text":"Now, just think of the early 1960's in China."},{"time":732000,"text":"Over a lifetime, through everything,"},{"time":735000,"text":"through the Cultural Revolution and everything afterward,"},{"time":738000,"text":"he's kept collecting,"},{"time":740000,"text":"so that he now has over eight million pieces"},{"time":742000,"text":"in his museums"},{"time":744000,"text":"documenting contemporary Chinese history."},{"time":748000,"text":"These are pieces that you won't find anywhere else in the world,"},{"time":751000,"text":"in part because they document parts of history"},{"time":754000,"text":"Chinese choose to forget."},{"time":757000,"text":"For example, he's got over one million pieces"},{"time":760000,"text":"documenting the Sino-Japanese War,"},{"time":763000,"text":"a war that's not talked about in China very much"},{"time":765000,"text":"and whose heroes are not honored."},{"time":768000,"text":"Why did he do all this?"},{"time":770000,"text":"Because he thought"},{"time":773000,"text":"a nation should never repeat the mistakes of the past."}]},{"cues":[{"time":776000,"text":"So, from commissioning"},{"time":779000,"text":"slightly larger than life bronze statues"},{"time":781000,"text":"of the heroes of the Sino-Japanese War,"},{"time":784000,"text":"including those Chinese"},{"time":786000,"text":"who then fought with each other"},{"time":788000,"text":"and left mainland China to go to Taiwan,"},{"time":791000,"text":"to commemorating all the unknown,"},{"time":794000,"text":"ordinary soldiers who survived,"},{"time":797000,"text":"by asking them to take prints of their hands,"},{"time":800000,"text":"he is making sure -- one man is making sure --"},{"time":803000,"text":"that history is not forgotten."},{"time":805000,"text":"But it's not just Chinese heroes he cares about."},{"time":808000,"text":"This building contains the world's largest collection"},{"time":811000,"text":"of documents and artifacts"},{"time":813000,"text":"commemorating the U.S. role"},{"time":815000,"text":"in fighting on the Chinese side"},{"time":817000,"text":"in that long war --"},{"time":819000,"text":"the Flying Tigers."},{"time":822000,"text":"He has nine other buildings --"},{"time":824000,"text":"that are already open to the public --"},{"time":826000,"text":"filled to the rafters with artifacts"},{"time":829000,"text":"documenting contemporary Chinese history."},{"time":833000,"text":"Two of the most sensitive buildings"},{"time":835000,"text":"include a lifetime of collection"},{"time":837000,"text":"about the Cultural Revolution,"},{"time":839000,"text":"a period that actually most Chinese"},{"time":841000,"text":"would prefer to forget."},{"time":843000,"text":"But he doesn't want his nation"},{"time":845000,"text":"ever to forget."}]},{"cues":[{"time":848000,"text":"These people inspire me,"},{"time":850000,"text":"and they inspire me because they show us"},{"time":853000,"text":"what is possible when you change the way"},{"time":855000,"text":"you look at the world,"},{"time":857000,"text":"change the way you look at your place in the world."},{"time":861000,"text":"They looked outside,"},{"time":863000,"text":"and then they changed what was on the inside."},{"time":865000,"text":"They didn't go to business school."},{"time":867000,"text":"They didn't read a manual, \"How to Be a Good Leader"},{"time":869000,"text":"in 10 Easy Steps.\""},{"time":872000,"text":"But they have qualities we'd all recognize."},{"time":875000,"text":"They have drive, passion, commitment."},{"time":878000,"text":"They've gone away"},{"time":880000,"text":"from what they did before,"},{"time":882000,"text":"and they've gone"},{"time":884000,"text":"to something they didn't know."},{"time":886000,"text":"They've tried to connect worlds"},{"time":889000,"text":"they didn't know existed before."},{"time":891000,"text":"They've built bridges, and they've walked across them."},{"time":894000,"text":"They have a sense of the great arc of time"},{"time":896000,"text":"and their tiny place in it."},{"time":898000,"text":"They know people have come before them"},{"time":900000,"text":"and will follow them."},{"time":903000,"text":"And they know that they're part of a whole,"},{"time":905000,"text":"that they depend on other people."},{"time":907000,"text":"It's not about them, they know that,"},{"time":909000,"text":"but it has to start with them."},{"time":911000,"text":"And they have humility."},{"time":913000,"text":"It just happens."}]},{"cues":[{"time":917000,"text":"But we know it doesn't just happen, don't we?"},{"time":920000,"text":"We know it takes a lot to make it happen,"},{"time":922000,"text":"and we know the direction the world is going in."},{"time":925000,"text":"So I think we need succession planning"},{"time":928000,"text":"on a global basis."},{"time":931000,"text":"We can't wait for the next generation, the new joiners,"},{"time":934000,"text":"to come in and learn how to be the good leaders we need."},{"time":936000,"text":"I think it has to start with us."},{"time":938000,"text":"And we know, just like they knew,"},{"time":940000,"text":"how hard it is."},{"time":943000,"text":"But the good news is that we don't have to figure it out as we go along;"},{"time":946000,"text":"we have models, we have examples,"},{"time":949000,"text":"like Benki and Sanghamitra and Jianchuan."},{"time":952000,"text":"We can look at what they've done, if we look."},{"time":955000,"text":"We can learn from what they've learned."},{"time":958000,"text":"We can change the way we see ourselves in the world."},{"time":962000,"text":"And if we're lucky,"},{"time":964000,"text":"we can change the way"},{"time":966000,"text":"our great-grandchildren"},{"time":968000,"text":"will answer Benki's question."}]},{"cues":[{"time":971000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":973000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}